{"tid":1698562,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"<2019年，我獲得一本只殺警察的死亡筆記>","createTime":"2019-11-07T14:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T05:46:06.000Z","uid":59450,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3085415008af64fa48652803b8c769f244fb7caf","tid":1698562,"uid":59450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:42:35.000Z","msg":"地下出現一本名為&lt;警察死亡筆記&gt;嘅簿，我心諗，我今次仲唔執到？我鍾意警察點死都得啦！<br />\n<br />\n黑警做咁多陰質野，我一定要佢地血債血償！<br />\n<br />\n我翻開第一頁：<br />\n<br />\n1、名字/警察編號被寫在死亡筆記本裡的人會死掉。"},{"pid":"ed94c763551730afdd872bd98798a15b71cb2635","tid":1698562,"uid":59450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:45:48.000Z","msg":"屌你，我點撚知呀？個個都唔show架喎而家。<br />\n<br />\n冷靜啲，我冇咁容易放棄！<br />\n<br />\n我記得我可以換死神眼球，咁一望就知佢地啲名啦。<br />\n<br />\n我揭後幾頁：<br />\n<br />\n17、死亡筆記本的所有者，可以自己所剩餘壽命的一半換得死神的眼球。用死神的眼球看著人類的臉，就能看到那個人的姓名與壽命。"},{"pid":"a15754d9bb76eac6f62b93408a404250c2597536","tid":1698562,"uid":59450,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:49:06.000Z","msg":"我撕晒所有紙出嚟，逐頁逐頁撕。<br />\n<br />\n將佢哋撕做正方形紙。<br />\n<br />\n果晚，我去咗新城市廣場摺紙鶴。<br />\n<br />\n&lt;完&gt;"},{"pid":"2817b2df3e33c1f3dd6d8933eb3ad8bf4aec203b","tid":1698562,"uid":40820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a15754d9bb76eac6f62b93408a404250c2597536","tid":1698562,"uid":59450,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:49:06.000Z","msg":"我撕晒所有紙出嚟，逐頁逐頁撕。<br />\n<br />\n將佢哋撕做正方形紙。<br />\n<br />\n果晚，我去咗新城市廣場摺紙鶴。<br />\n<br />\n&lt;完&gt;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:01:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6866584a3f6146faf36b653ea99b490a3cac82c6","tid":1698562,"uid":222269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:54:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0001273be8351103ca11e273efff1dcc8b28bf5e","tid":1698562,"uid":59450,"li